Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.50,Persona 5-hm1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\b1\fs130\c&H000000&\bord0\blur10\4c&H08081A&\fn思源宋体 CN\pos(968,682.667)}4月9日星期六{\b0}
